        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Trauma-Informed Schools Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill provides for the&nbsp;use of trauma-informed practices in public elementary and secondary schools and allows states to use certain federal funds to train teachers in such practices.</p>]]></text>
